Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.00,0:00:05.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能賜我一個法名嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.71,0:00:07.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜信失蹤了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.32,0:00:11.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你們也屍變了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.03,0:00:14.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是殺死你女兒的犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.47,0:00:25.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海鷗的水兵先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.63,0:00:30.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼 好疼好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.97,0:00:31.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.97,0:00:34.24,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公 我切到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.42,0:00:35.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流了好多血呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.80,0:00:41.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦 是你太誇張啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.90,0:00:42.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
